    {
      "id": "0e50cae6-eed9-4002-bf55-a56edb9e3a18",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Universities are constantly look into ways to improve the academic performance of their students and the introduiction of VLEs represents a significant step toward that direction. Authors use VLE data to create an early warning system that makes recommendations for intervention. ",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "0e50cae6-eed9-4002-bf55-a56edb9e3a18",
