    {
      "id": "a356054e-873b-4385-9963-5ba188baf530",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Authors perform pre-processing on the data and use ISMOTE to deal with data imbalance. Authors feed the preprocessed data as input to a EDL_KDL mode, a deep learning explainable model to predict performance and that can be explained using SHAP values. This model achieves 99.6% accuracy and 99.21% precision on OULAD. ",
